{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then any call to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"explicitNotify"},{"type":"text","text":", then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_signal_connect()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"(C Language Example):"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleSignalName\/notify"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/typemodulesignalname\/notify"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Case","symbolKind":"case","title":"TypeModuleSignalName.notify","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"externalID":"s:10GLibObject20TypeModuleSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleSignalName"]]},"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"abstract":[],"title":"GLibObject","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/TypeModuleSignalName":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"TypeModuleSignalName"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/typemodulesignalname","kind":"symbol","title":"TypeModuleSignalName","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleSignalName","role":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"TypeModuleSignalName"}]},"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names":{"url":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"canonical parameter names","type":"text"}],"title":"canonical parameter names"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/TypeModuleSignalName/notify":{"kind":"symbol","title":"TypeModuleSignalName.notify","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"notify"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/typemodulesignalname\/notify","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/TypeModuleSignalName\/notify","abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol"}}}